longBusinessSummary: Catena AB (publ) owns, develops, manages, and sells logistics properties in Sweden and Denmark. It provides complexity terminals for immediate transshipment; logistics warehouses for storage; distribution centers; warehouses for cold storage; fully automated warehouses; omni warehouses; and city logistics. The company was founded in 1967 and is headquartered in Helsingborg, Sweden.
